nodes.text: Star Wars: Rebel Force is a series of six young-reader novels written by Alex Wheeler. Set between Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope and Star Wars: Episode V The Empire Strikes Back, the series features Luke Skywalker, Leia Organa, and Han Solo.

It is a critical moment in the struggle between the Rebels and the Empire: the Force itself hangs in the balance, and all the hopes of the galaxy depend on the adventures of Luke Skywalker, Princess Leia, Han Solo, and a host of other heroes.
